{"tid":2225500,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★逾200人迫入長洲度中秋「諗住嚟到可以吸新鮮空氣","createTime":"2020-10-01T11:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T04:09:04.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9f800a2bd42b6a76c3bbe2123a03691590f4951e","tid":2225500,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:16:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/5390111/org/fe3bbe7c5a40c54e0d8e8e50836998c5.jpg/P1DlLk-NJHiYPc0CI8wDGlZ52EJYu3htyDvmQOI75kA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F5390111%2Forg%2Ffe3bbe7c5a40c54e0d8e8e50836998c5.jpg%2FP1DlLk-NJHiYPc0CI8wDGlZ52EJYu3htyDvmQOI75kA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=0b4f4479&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中環碼頭往長洲方向，一早有約200多人排隊乘船到長洲度假耍樂，當中不少為一家大細及來港工作內容，亦有不少年輕人趁假期結伴同遊。<br />\n<br />\n黃小姐與子女及多名親友到長洲遊玩，同樣表示未有想有這府多人會一同到離島，「諗住嚟到可以吸新鮮空氣，但係而家人咁多，空氣都唔夠清新啦！」疫情之下，不少人選擇居家抗疫，黃説自己已經跟子女困在家中多日，非常苦悶，假期更已安排不同的活動跟他們去感受一下，「日日你眼望我眼，小朋友悶，我都好悶，我都要放下假！」笑言若非受到疫情影響，現時必定已經離港渡假，「我呢一刻好想去泰國，好想即刻衝出香港，離開香港！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/530774/%E9%80%BE200%E4%BA%BA%E8%BF%AB%E5%85%A5%E9%95%B7%E6%B4%B2%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%8B-%E6%9D%B1%E5%A0%A4%E6%88%BF%E5%83%B9%E8%B6%81%E6%97%BA%E5%8A%A0%E5%83%B93%E5%80%8D-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91-%E5%A5%BD%E6%83%B3%E5%8E%BB%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F530774%2F%25E9%2580%25BE200%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25BF%25AB%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25A7%258B-%25E6%259D%25B1%25E5%25A0%25A4%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%2583%25B9%25E8%25B6%2581%25E6%2597%25BA%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%2583%25B93%25E5%2580%258D-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E6%2583%25B3%25E5%258E%25BB%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E5%259C%258B&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1yq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=a0d86c6a\" data-auto-link target=\"